data.description: Take a walk down Spann to check out this perfectly located Fountain Square beauty. Buyers will fall in love with the home's front porch, perfect for a morning or evening enjoying the neighborhood. Home also boasts a fully fenced backyard and deck space. With 4 bedrooms, separate kitchen and dining spaces, double closets in the primary bedroom, and 2 full baths + laundry on the second floor, you won't want for functional living. Home sits on a quiet, newly paved street that's less than a mile from most neighborhood dining and entertainment options as well as a great neighborhood school. You'll have the choice of walking or biking to your daily activities, the location truly can't be beat!
